  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        Patients that had a preoperative investigation because of communicating hydrocephalus. MRI
        revealed ventriculomegaly (Evans ratio &gt; 0.3), no obstruction to CSF flow at visual
        inspection. Most, but not all, fulfilled the criteria of &quot;probable&quot; or &quot;possible&quot; INPH.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  preoperative investigation because of communicating hydrocephalus

          -  ventriculomegaly (Evans ratio &gt; 0.3)

          -  no obstruction to CSF flow at visual inspection

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  postoperative infusion test investigations

          -  patients that were unable to understand instructions
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
